WEBVTT

00:00:06.112 --> 00:00:07.114
[rock music]

00:00:07.114 --> 00:00:15.197
♪ ♪

00:00:21.309 --> 00:00:22.311
[woman singing in Japanese]

00:00:22.311 --> 00:00:30.160
♪ ♪

00:01:42.572 --> 00:01:43.841
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WITH LORDGENOME’S

00:01:43.841 --> 00:01:45.712
DEFEAT, HUMANITY WAS FREE TO

00:01:45.712 --> 00:01:47.448
COME UP TO THE SURFACE AND

00:01:47.448 --> 00:01:48.183
THRIVE.

00:01:48.183 --> 00:01:50.420
WHAT ARE LAGANN, THE CORE DRILL,

00:01:50.420 --> 00:01:51.757
AND SPIRAL POWER?

00:01:51.757 --> 00:01:54.195
WHY DID LORDGENOME TRY TO DRIVE

00:01:54.195 --> 00:01:56.199
HUMANITY UNDERGROUND?

00:01:56.199 --> 00:01:57.669
ALL THOSE MYSTERIES AND MORE

00:01:57.669 --> 00:02:00.207
REMAIN UNSOLVED.

00:02:00.207 --> 00:02:02.411
BUT ALL OF US ARE INTENT NOW ON

00:02:02.411 --> 00:02:03.279
BUILDING NEW LIVES

00:02:03.279 --> 00:02:04.650
FOR OURSELVES.

00:02:04.650 --> 00:02:06.820
SO WE FOCUS ON TOMORROW’S HOPES,

00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:08.591
NOT YESTERDAY’S LINGERING

00:02:08.591 --> 00:02:10.327
QUESTIONS.

00:02:10.327 --> 00:02:11.764
ONE OF THE FEW RIDDLES WE DID

00:02:11.764 --> 00:02:13.299
SOLVE IS OLD COCO’S

00:02:13.299 --> 00:02:14.268
TRUE IDENTITY.

00:02:14.268 --> 00:02:15.505
APPARENTLY, HE WAS A BEASTMAN

00:02:15.505 --> 00:02:17.642
CREATED TO SERVE AS NIA’S

00:02:17.642 --> 00:02:18.878
BUTLER, AND THAT’S WHY HE HAD

00:02:18.878 --> 00:02:20.380
ALWAYS LOOKED AFTER HER.

00:02:20.380 --> 00:02:22.151
IS IT BECAUSE WE’RE AT PEACE

00:02:22.151 --> 00:02:23.219
THAT WE’VE ONLY SOLVED SUCH

00:02:23.219 --> 00:02:26.259
TRIVIAL MYSTERIES?

00:02:26.259 --> 00:02:28.597
YES, WE HAVE ALL BASKED IN THIS

00:02:28.597 --> 00:02:30.434
PEACE FOR SEVEN YEARS,

00:02:30.434 --> 00:02:32.471
PRETENDING ALL THE WHILE NOT TO

00:02:32.471 --> 00:02:34.609
NOTICE LORDGENOME’S DYING WORDS

00:02:34.609 --> 00:02:35.745
GNAWING AWAY AT US FROM

00:02:35.745 --> 00:02:37.281
THE INSIDE.

00:02:37.281 --> 00:02:40.354
[musical beeps]

00:02:46.934 --> 00:02:49.639
[sighs]

00:02:49.639 --> 00:02:51.309
&gt;&gt; Simon: HAVE A HEART, ROSSIU.

00:02:51.309 --> 00:02:51.877
COME ON.

00:02:51.877 --> 00:02:53.179
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: THESE ARE ALL CITIZEN

00:02:53.179 --> 00:02:54.248
COMPLAINTS.

00:02:54.248 --> 00:02:55.283
THE SEWERS ARE BACKED UP, TAXES

00:02:55.283 --> 00:02:57.287
ARE TOO HIGH, NEIGHBORS ARE

00:02:57.287 --> 00:02:57.822
TOO NOISY.

00:02:57.822 --> 00:02:59.893
IT’S ALL SELF‐CENTERED NONSENSE.

00:02:59.893 --> 00:03:01.229
THEY’VE COMPLETELY FORGOTTEN

00:03:01.229 --> 00:03:03.400
WHAT LIFE WAS LIKE IN THE PITS.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.203
&gt;&gt; Simon: I THINK THAT’S GREAT.

00:03:05.203 --> 00:03:05.938
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IS IT, THOUGH?

00:03:05.938 --> 00:03:07.642
&gt;&gt; Simon: IS SOMETHING

00:03:07.642 --> 00:03:08.677
BOTHERING YOU?

00:03:08.677 --> 00:03:09.613
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NO, SIR.

00:03:09.613 --> 00:03:13.286
[door chimes]

00:03:13.286 --> 00:03:14.388
&gt;&gt; Nia: WELL MET, YOU TWO!

00:03:14.388 --> 00:03:15.858
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA, HEY, WHAT’S UP?

00:03:15.858 --> 00:03:17.562
&gt;&gt; Nia: SURPRISE, I MADE YOU

00:03:17.562 --> 00:03:21.737
LUNCH!

00:03:21.737 --> 00:03:23.708
I’M SORRY, ROSSIU.

00:03:23.708 --> 00:03:25.243
I FORGOT TO MAKE A LUNCH

00:03:25.243 --> 00:03:25.845
FOR YOU.

00:03:25.845 --> 00:03:26.780
I’LL RUSH OUT AND MAKE SOMETHING

00:03:26.780 --> 00:03:27.515
RIGHT NOW.

00:03:27.515 --> 00:03:29.185
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NO, THAT’S QUITE

00:03:29.185 --> 00:03:29.553
ALL RIGHT.

00:03:29.553 --> 00:03:30.722
THERE’S A COUNCIL MEETING

00:03:30.722 --> 00:03:31.523
IN 15 MINUTES.

00:03:31.523 --> 00:03:33.527
TRY TO FINISH LUNCH BY THEN,

00:03:33.527 --> 00:03:34.629
OKAY?

00:03:45.585 --> 00:03:52.364
[rocket rumbling]

00:03:52.364 --> 00:03:55.638
[cheers]

00:03:55.638 --> 00:03:56.907
&gt;&gt; Ron: THIS IS YOUR HUMBLE

00:03:56.907 --> 00:03:58.343
LEERON, SCIENCE BUREAU CHIEF!

00:03:58.343 --> 00:03:59.746
THE LAUNCH OF OUR MOON PROBE

00:03:59.746 --> 00:04:01.349
GUNROCKET WAS COMPLETELY

00:04:01.349 --> 00:04:02.284
SUCCESSFUL.

00:04:02.284 --> 00:04:03.353
IT’LL ARRIVE AT THE MOON IN JUST

00:04:03.353 --> 00:04:03.988
ONE DAY.

00:04:03.988 --> 00:04:05.457
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: THAT’S GOOD NEWS.

00:04:05.457 --> 00:04:06.560
PLEASE SUBMIT YOUR FORMAL REPORT

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:07.428
LATER TODAY.

00:04:07.428 --> 00:04:08.396
&gt;&gt; Ron: OKAY.

00:04:08.396 --> 00:04:10.267
FROM LEERON WITH LOVE.

00:04:10.267 --> 00:04:13.507
CIAO.

00:04:13.507 --> 00:04:16.379
&gt;&gt; Kittan: AW, COME ON.

00:04:16.379 --> 00:04:17.347
DO YOU REALLY THINK YOU’RE GONNA

00:04:17.347 --> 00:04:18.416
FIND SOMETHING UP THERE, SIMON?

00:04:18.416 --> 00:04:19.753
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: ADDRESS HIM AS

00:04:19.753 --> 00:04:21.557
SUPREME COMMANDER, LEGAL AFFAIRS

00:04:21.557 --> 00:04:22.357
BUREAU CHIEF KITTAN.

00:04:22.357 --> 00:04:23.627
&gt;&gt; Kittan: ALL RIGHT.

00:04:23.627 --> 00:04:25.665
&gt;&gt; Simon: HE SAID A MILLION

00:04:25.665 --> 00:04:26.767
APES.

00:04:26.767 --> 00:04:28.871
WHEN THE LAND OVERFLOWS WITH

00:04:28.871 --> 00:04:30.407
A MILLION APES, THE MOON SHALL

00:04:30.407 --> 00:04:31.777
BECOME HELL’S MESSENGER AND

00:04:31.777 --> 00:04:34.381
DESTROY THE WORLD OF THE SPIRAL.

00:04:34.381 --> 00:04:35.985
THOSE WERE LORDGENOME’S

00:04:35.985 --> 00:04:38.891
DYING WORDS.

00:04:38.891 --> 00:04:40.427
THINKING ABOUT IT HASN’T GOTTEN

00:04:40.427 --> 00:04:41.028
US ANYWHERE.

00:04:41.028 --> 00:04:42.464
WE HAVE TO GO.

00:04:42.464 --> 00:04:44.468
AND IF WE DON’T FIND ANYTHING,

00:04:44.468 --> 00:04:44.936
NO HARM DONE.

00:04:44.936 --> 00:04:46.540
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: YOU KNOW, THIS IS

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:47.374
PRETTY AMAZING.

00:04:47.374 --> 00:04:49.513
SEVEN YEARS AGO, WE DIDN’T EVEN

00:04:49.513 --> 00:04:50.413
KNOW THE MOON WAS A SATELLITE OF

00:04:50.413 --> 00:04:51.349
OUR WORLD.

00:04:51.349 --> 00:04:52.552
AND NOW WE’RE CAPABLE OF SENDING

00:04:52.552 --> 00:04:53.554
PROBES THERE.

00:04:53.554 --> 00:04:55.390
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: CITIZEN AFFAIRS

00:04:55.390 --> 00:04:56.392
SECRETARY JORGUN, HOW IS THE

00:04:56.392 --> 00:04:57.795
CENSUS PROCEEDING TO DATE?

00:04:57.795 --> 00:04:59.766
&gt;&gt; Jorgun: YEAH, ABOUT THAT‐‐

00:04:59.766 --> 00:05:01.035
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: THE "MILLION APES" IN

00:05:01.035 --> 00:05:02.437
LORDGENOME’S PROPHECY REFERS TO

00:05:02.437 --> 00:05:03.406
US HUMANS.

00:05:03.406 --> 00:05:04.743
IT IS VITAL THAT WE DETERMINE

00:05:04.743 --> 00:05:06.379
WHEN THE PLANET’S POPULATION

00:05:06.379 --> 00:05:09.619
WILL REACH 1 MILLION PEOPLE.

00:05:09.619 --> 00:05:10.453
AND WE MUST DO IT IMMEDIATELY.

00:05:10.453 --> 00:05:12.525
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: TAKE IT EASY, ROSSIU.

00:05:12.525 --> 00:05:13.727
IT’S A MISTAKE TO HAVE THESE TWO

00:05:13.727 --> 00:05:14.996
TRY AND COUNT ANYTHING MORE THAN

00:05:14.996 --> 00:05:15.698
THEIR FINGERS.

00:05:15.698 --> 00:05:17.401
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NO ONE IS SUGGESTING

00:05:17.401 --> 00:05:18.504
THEY DO THE COUNT THEMSELVES.

00:05:18.504 --> 00:05:20.440
USE THE ORGANIZATION TO DO IT.

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:21.375
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: I’M JUST SAYIN’ THAT

00:05:21.375 --> 00:05:22.812
THESE TWO CAN’T HANDLE

00:05:22.812 --> 00:05:24.048
A DELICATE JOB LIKE THAT,

00:05:24.048 --> 00:05:24.716
ALL RIGHT?

00:05:24.716 --> 00:05:25.518
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YOU KNOW, I WANT TO

00:05:25.518 --> 00:05:26.620
KNOW WHY YOU PEOPLE STAY WORKING

00:05:26.620 --> 00:05:27.989
IN THE GOVERNMENT.

00:05:27.989 --> 00:05:29.058
AT EVERY COUNCIL MEETING,

00:05:29.058 --> 00:05:30.561
ALL YOU DO IS KICK BACK!

00:05:30.561 --> 00:05:31.663
IS THAT WHAT YOUR JOB IS?

00:05:31.663 --> 00:05:33.099
THOSE WHO TOLD US THEY COULDN’T

00:05:33.099 --> 00:05:34.435
HANDLE THE JOB AND JUST LEFT

00:05:34.435 --> 00:05:36.573
WERE A LOT MORE HONEST!

00:05:36.573 --> 00:05:37.642
&gt;&gt; Jorgun: UH, SAY WHAT?

00:05:37.642 --> 00:05:38.511
&gt;&gt; Balinbow: SAY WHAT?

00:05:38.511 --> 00:05:39.044
&gt;&gt; Simon: GIVE IT A REST,

00:05:39.044 --> 00:05:41.082
EVERYONE.

00:05:41.082 --> 00:05:42.819
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IS IT ALL RIGHT IF I

00:05:42.819 --> 00:05:44.523
ISSUE ORDERS TO THE CITIZEN

00:05:44.523 --> 00:05:44.990
AFFAIRS BUREAU?

00:05:44.990 --> 00:05:46.092
&gt;&gt; Simon: GO AHEAD.

00:05:46.092 --> 00:05:47.529
[groaning]

00:05:47.529 --> 00:05:48.864
RELAX, GUYS.

00:05:48.864 --> 00:05:50.501
THERE ISN’T GONNA BE ANY CHANGE

00:05:50.501 --> 00:05:52.639
IN YOUR STATUS BECAUSE OF THIS.

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:53.841
WE’RE JUST GONNA LET ROSSIU

00:05:53.841 --> 00:05:54.776
OVERSEE THIS ONE.

00:05:54.776 --> 00:05:59.819
THAT’S ALL.

00:05:59.819 --> 00:06:00.988
&gt;&gt; Jorgun: WHO DOES THAT

00:06:00.988 --> 00:06:02.625
BIG SHOT ROSSIU THINK HE IS?

00:06:02.625 --> 00:06:03.459
&gt;&gt; Balinbow: WE GOT SOMETHING

00:06:03.459 --> 00:06:03.827
TO OFFER!

00:06:03.827 --> 00:06:04.663
WE GOT A LOT TO OFFER!

00:06:04.663 --> 00:06:07.835
[both growling, chomping]

00:06:07.835 --> 00:06:08.938
&gt;&gt; Chief: AH, LOOK AT THESE

00:06:08.938 --> 00:06:09.873
TWO FINE NOTABLES OF THE NEW

00:06:09.873 --> 00:06:12.579
GOVERNMENT.

00:06:12.579 --> 00:06:14.616
NO ONE EATS QUITE LIKE YOU DO.

00:06:14.616 --> 00:06:16.987
FEEL FREE TO EAT ALL YOU LIKE!

00:06:16.987 --> 00:06:18.924
AFTER ALL, KAMINA AND SIMON, OUR

00:06:18.924 --> 00:06:21.095
BELOVED HEROES, BOTH GREW UP

00:06:21.095 --> 00:06:22.632
STRONG AND HEALTHY EATING MY

00:06:22.632 --> 00:06:24.435
FAMOUS PIG‐MOLE STEAKS!

00:06:24.435 --> 00:06:26.773
I RAISED THOSE BOYS AS IF THEY

00:06:26.773 --> 00:06:27.474
WERE MY OWN!

00:06:27.474 --> 00:06:32.484
[laughs]

00:06:32.484 --> 00:06:33.554
&gt;&gt; Kittan: YOU KNOW, WITH HIM

00:06:33.554 --> 00:06:34.923
HANGING AROUND, YOU WOULDN’T

00:06:34.923 --> 00:06:36.058
NEED TO BE KAMINA TO WANT

00:06:36.058 --> 00:06:36.793
TO ESCAPE.

00:06:36.793 --> 00:06:37.629
[sighs]

00:06:37.629 --> 00:06:38.731
HEY, WHAT’S THE MATTER?

00:06:38.731 --> 00:06:39.799
YOU LOOK KINDA BUMMED OUT.

00:06:39.799 --> 00:06:43.540
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: HMM.

00:06:43.540 --> 00:06:45.477
A MILLION APES, HUH?

00:06:45.477 --> 00:06:46.813
&gt;&gt; Kittan: THE SPIRAL KING WAS

00:06:46.813 --> 00:06:47.749
JUST MESSING WITH US.

00:06:47.749 --> 00:06:49.385
YOU GOTTA TAKE THAT WITH A BIG

00:06:49.385 --> 00:06:50.487
GRAIN OF SALT.

00:06:50.487 --> 00:06:52.457
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: DUMB‐ASS, HAVE YOU

00:06:52.457 --> 00:06:53.527
GONE COMPLETELY CLUELESS?

00:06:53.527 --> 00:06:54.896
DAYAKKA’S WORRIED ABOUT HIS KID.

00:06:54.896 --> 00:06:55.998
&gt;&gt; Kittan: OH, RIGHT.

00:06:55.998 --> 00:06:57.134
IT’S JUST ABOUT DUE.

00:06:57.134 --> 00:06:58.469
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: HEY, KITTAN, HOW CAN

00:06:58.469 --> 00:06:59.606
YOU BE SO RELAXED ABOUT IT?

00:06:59.606 --> 00:07:01.442
YOU’RE JUST ABOUT TO BE

00:07:01.442 --> 00:07:02.512
AN UNCLE, MAN.

00:07:02.512 --> 00:07:03.714
&gt;&gt; Kittan: IT HASN’T REALLY

00:07:03.714 --> 00:07:06.987
SUNK IN YET.

00:07:06.987 --> 00:07:08.189
♪ COME TRY THE PIG‐MOLE STEAK ♪

00:07:08.189 --> 00:07:09.960
♪ THAT GURREN LAGANN LOVES ♪

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:11.128
♪ YOUR MOUTH WILL WATER ♪

00:07:11.128 --> 00:07:12.064
♪ WITH EACH BITE... ♪ ♪

00:07:12.064 --> 00:07:13.132
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: HEY, SIS!

00:07:13.132 --> 00:07:15.771
YOU WANT THE LAUNDRY OVER HERE?

00:07:15.771 --> 00:07:17.040
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: YEAH, THAT’S FINE.

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:18.042
THANKS.

00:07:18.042 --> 00:07:19.679
[doorbell rings]

00:07:19.679 --> 00:07:20.815
COMING!

00:07:20.815 --> 00:07:22.117
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: I’VE GOT IT!

00:07:22.117 --> 00:07:23.821
YOU SIT RIGHT THERE AND RELAX!

00:07:23.821 --> 00:07:29.532
[gasps]

00:07:29.532 --> 00:07:30.668
HE PROPOSED?

00:07:30.668 --> 00:07:32.705
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: HE PROPOSED?

00:07:32.705 --> 00:07:33.707
&gt;&gt; Nia: THAT’S RIGHT.

00:07:33.707 --> 00:07:35.544
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: WELL, WELL, SIMON

00:07:35.544 --> 00:07:36.546
FINALLY WENT AND TOOK THE

00:07:36.546 --> 00:07:37.447
PLUNGE, DID HE?

00:07:37.447 --> 00:07:38.984
&gt;&gt; Nia: THAT’S WHY I CAME FOR

00:07:38.984 --> 00:07:39.886
YOUR ADVICE.

00:07:39.886 --> 00:07:40.988
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: TELL US, WHAT DID HE

00:07:40.988 --> 00:07:41.823
SAY TO YOU?

00:07:41.823 --> 00:07:44.228
I HAVE TO KNOW!

00:07:48.671 --> 00:07:52.578
[footsteps approach]

00:07:52.578 --> 00:07:53.781
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT’S BEAUTIFUL,

00:07:53.781 --> 00:07:54.114
ISN’T IT?

00:07:54.114 --> 00:07:54.883
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT?

00:07:54.883 --> 00:07:57.789
&gt;&gt; Simon: THE CITY.

00:07:57.789 --> 00:07:59.659
&gt;&gt; Nia: YES.

00:07:59.659 --> 00:08:00.995
&gt;&gt; Simon: EVERYONE IS LIVING

00:08:00.995 --> 00:08:02.832
HAPPY LIVES UNDER THE SUN.

00:08:02.832 --> 00:08:06.606
&gt;&gt; Nia: YOU’RE RIGHT.

00:08:06.606 --> 00:08:07.742
&gt;&gt; Simon: MAYBE THE TIME IS

00:08:07.742 --> 00:08:08.977
FINALLY RIGHT TO GET OUT.

00:08:08.977 --> 00:08:10.614
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT?

00:08:10.614 --> 00:08:12.217
&gt;&gt; Simon: TIME TO FORGET THAT

00:08:12.217 --> 00:08:13.620
WE’RE A PRINCESS AND THE LEADER

00:08:13.620 --> 00:08:15.725
OF TEAM GURREN, TO SEE THE SAME

00:08:15.725 --> 00:08:17.628
THINGS, HEAR THE SAME SOUNDS,

00:08:17.628 --> 00:08:18.964
AND SHARE THE SAME LAUGHS.

00:08:18.964 --> 00:08:20.901
MAYBE IT WOULD BE NICE TO HAVE

00:08:20.901 --> 00:08:22.538
THAT KIND OF LIFE NOW.

00:08:22.538 --> 00:08:25.043
MY EYES WOULD BE YOUR EYES,

00:08:25.043 --> 00:08:27.214
AND YOUR EARS WOULD BE MY EARS.

00:08:27.214 --> 00:08:28.684
MAYBE SOMETHING LIKE THAT WOULD

00:08:28.684 --> 00:08:31.255
BE NICE.

00:08:31.255 --> 00:08:34.729
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT’S THIS?

00:08:34.729 --> 00:08:35.731
&gt;&gt; Simon: LET’S GET MARRIED,

00:08:35.731 --> 00:08:37.935
NIA.

00:08:37.935 --> 00:08:44.616
[sighs]

00:08:44.616 --> 00:08:47.588
&gt;&gt; Nia: NO WAY!

00:08:47.588 --> 00:08:48.857
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: YOU MEAN YOU

00:08:48.857 --> 00:08:49.692
TURNED HIM DOWN?

00:08:49.692 --> 00:08:50.528
&gt;&gt; Nia: THAT’S RIGHT.

00:08:50.528 --> 00:08:52.097
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: WHY DID YOU GO AND

00:08:52.097 --> 00:08:52.832
DO THAT?

00:08:52.832 --> 00:08:53.767
&gt;&gt; Nia: HMM?

00:08:53.767 --> 00:08:55.504
WELL, I THOUGHT THAT MAYBE TWO

00:08:55.504 --> 00:08:57.074
PEOPLE REALLY COULDN’T BECOME

00:08:57.074 --> 00:08:58.276
THE SAME PERSON.

00:08:58.276 --> 00:09:01.248
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: OH, BROTHER.

00:09:01.248 --> 00:09:03.654
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: YES, THAT’S TRUE.

00:09:03.654 --> 00:09:04.589
BUT THAT’S BASICALLY WHAT

00:09:04.589 --> 00:09:05.791
MARRIED COUPLES ARE.

00:09:05.791 --> 00:09:07.528
ANYWAY, HE ONLY MEANT IT

00:09:07.528 --> 00:09:08.731
AS A FIGURE OF SPEECH.

00:09:08.731 --> 00:09:09.733
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: SIS, BE CAREFUL WITH

00:09:09.733 --> 00:09:10.568
THE BABY!

00:09:10.568 --> 00:09:12.270
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: SIMON, THE BOY WHO’S

00:09:12.270 --> 00:09:13.774
ONLY GOOD AT DIGGING TUNNELS AND

00:09:13.774 --> 00:09:15.276
FIGHTING IN GURREN LAGANN, SPENT

00:09:15.276 --> 00:09:16.813
SEVEN YEARS TRYING TO GET THOSE

00:09:16.813 --> 00:09:17.682
WORDS OUT!

00:09:17.682 --> 00:09:19.619
SO WHAT ABOUT YOU, NIA?

00:09:19.619 --> 00:09:21.656
HOW DO YOU FEEL ABOUT HIM?

00:09:21.656 --> 00:09:24.261
&gt;&gt; Nia: HOW DO I FEEL ABOUT HIM?

00:09:24.261 --> 00:09:25.765
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: YES, IT’S IMPORTANT

00:09:25.765 --> 00:09:27.100
WHAT THE WORDS MAKE YOU FEEL,

00:09:27.100 --> 00:09:30.206
NOT WHAT THEY MEAN.

00:09:38.757 --> 00:09:40.026
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: GUESS WE GOT OUR

00:09:40.026 --> 00:09:40.628
