&gt;&gt; Rossiu: HANDGUNS AND BLADES

00:19:05.691 --> 00:19:06.526
HAVE NO EFFECT AT ALL!

00:19:06.526 --> 00:19:08.162
&gt;&gt; Kittan: ROSSIU, WHAT ARE

00:19:08.162 --> 00:19:08.495
YOU DOING?

00:19:08.495 --> 00:19:11.536
[gunfire]

00:19:11.536 --> 00:19:16.445
[whirring]

00:19:16.445 --> 00:19:17.581
[rumbling]

00:19:17.581 --> 00:19:18.449
&gt;&gt; Darry: GIMMY!

00:19:18.449 --> 00:19:19.852
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: I’M OKAY!

00:19:19.852 --> 00:19:20.554
IT’S STILL WORKING!

