&gt;&gt; Guinble: GUNMEN ARE RELICS OF

00:19:33.178 --> 00:19:34.247
THE SPIRAL KING.

00:19:34.247 --> 00:19:35.550
THEY DIDN’T FIT IN WITH THE NEW

00:19:35.550 --> 00:19:37.487
ERA, SO WE DISPOSED OF

00:19:37.487 --> 00:19:38.188
ALL OF THEM.

