&gt;&gt; Kinon: THE GRAPEARLS ARE

00:19:38.757 --> 00:19:40.927
MASS‐PRODUCED COMBAT UNITS BASED

00:19:40.927 --> 00:19:42.363
ON ALL OUR GURREN LAGANN

00:19:42.363 --> 00:19:43.232
RESEARCH.

