IF THE GRAPEARLS ARE NO MATCH

00:19:44.234 --> 00:19:46.405
FOR IT, YOUR OLD GUNMEN COULDN’T

00:19:46.405 --> 00:19:48.643
SO MUCH AS PUT A SCRATCH ON IT.

00:19:48.643 --> 00:19:50.614
&gt;&gt; Kittan: KINON, YOUR, UM,

00:19:50.614 --> 00:19:52.383
