[whirring]

00:19:56.526 --> 00:19:59.497
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: DARRY, THAT’S INSANE!

00:19:59.497 --> 00:20:00.700
&gt;&gt; Darry: IT’S NOT.

00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:04.441
I CAN STILL FIGHT!

00:20:04.441 --> 00:20:05.510
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: DARRY!

00:20:05.510 --> 00:20:12.290
[whimpers]

00:20:12.290 --> 00:20:14.762
&gt;&gt; Darry: GURREN LAGANN.

00:20:14.762 --> 00:20:16.632
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHAT TOOK YOU SO

00:20:16.632 --> 00:20:17.500
LONG, SIMON?

00:20:17.500 --> 00:20:18.870
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: COMMANDER, PLEASE,

00:20:18.870 --> 00:20:19.538
IT’S NOT SAFE!

00:20:19.538 --> 00:20:20.439
IT’S NOT YOUR JOB TO GO OUT AND

00:20:20.439 --> 00:20:22.544
FIGHT ON THE FRONT LINES!

00:20:22.544 --> 00:20:23.513
HOW MANY TIMES DO I HAVE TO TELL

00:20:23.513 --> 00:20:24.447
YOU THAT?

00:20:24.447 --> 00:20:26.953
&gt;&gt; Simon: DUMB‐ASS!

00:20:26.953 --> 00:20:28.890
PROTECTING THE CITY AND ALL

00:20:28.890 --> 00:20:30.594
ITS CITIZENS, THAT IS

00:20:30.594 --> 00:20:31.461
AND SHOULD ALWAYS BE

00:20:31.461 --> 00:20:31.929
OUR NUMBER‐ONE JOB.

00:20:31.929 --> 00:20:33.900
HAS ALL THIS PEACE MADE

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:34.735
YOU SOFT?

00:20:34.735 --> 00:20:35.637
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: BUT, SIR‐‐

00:20:35.637 --> 00:20:36.639
&gt;&gt; Simon: THIS IS THE ONE PLACE

00:20:36.639 --> 00:20:37.674
I CAN BE ME.

00:20:37.674 --> 00:20:39.812
&gt;&gt; Boota: BOOHEE!

00:20:39.812 --> 00:20:40.847
&gt;&gt; Simon: LET’S GO,

00:20:40.847 --> 00:20:43.620
YOU FACELESS BASTARD!

00:20:43.620 --> 00:20:45.356
GIGA DRILL BREAK!

