TO IDENTIFICATION!

00:21:02.958 --> 00:21:03.760
&gt;&gt; Simon: DAMN.

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:04.795
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IF POSSIBLE,

00:21:04.795 --> 00:21:06.632
CAPTURE IT.

00:21:06.632 --> 00:21:07.568
&gt;&gt; Simon: QUIT BUGGING ME!

00:21:07.568 --> 00:21:09.003
LIKE I HAVE TIME FOR THAT.

00:21:09.003 --> 00:21:09.872
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: SIMON!

00:21:09.872 --> 00:21:10.674
&gt;&gt; Darry: HIS DRILL, IT’S

00:21:10.674 --> 00:21:14.515
BUILDING UP ENERGY.

00:21:14.515 --> 00:21:15.617
&gt;&gt; Simon: THIS IS IT!

00:21:15.617 --> 00:21:16.919
I’M SICK OF YOU AND YOUR

00:21:16.919 --> 00:21:17.855
LIGHT SHOW!

