I’M TAKING THIS CRAPPY BEAM OF

00:21:19.491 --> 00:21:21.762
YOURS AND SHOVING IT HARD

00:21:21.762 --> 00:21:26.873
RIGHT DOWN YOUR THROAT!

00:21:26.873 --> 00:21:31.816
[whirring and beeping]

